Subject: drm/i915/dpio: Fix VLV DPIO PLL register dword numbering
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: e55f8dfa35ba9ffa344ebd47b65c5be2a4ee6675
